24 results</a>, surprising the market very negatively, with the stock trading down about 30% on the day after the release.</p> <p>The main negative surprise was a significant fall</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/972911896/image_972911896.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742134-torrid-q3-expectations-collapsed-it-now-approaches-an-interesting-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 23:12:41"}, {"id": "4742133", "title": "Potential Headwinds And Tailwinds For Canadian Stocks In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"2025 people learning to make money from their second job\" data-id=\"1727961968\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">primeimages/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Canadian markets had solid performance in 2024, but can that run continue into next year? Anthony Okolie discusses with Michael O\u2019Brien, Managing Director and Head of the Core Canadian Equity Team at TD Asset Management.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1727961968/image_1727961968.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742133-potential-headwinds-tailwinds-for-canadian-stocks-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 23:10:00"}, {"id": "4742131", "title": "Relief For Heron Therapeutics After The Court Win On Cinvanti", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"gavel\" data-id=\"174197278\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174197278/image_174197278.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw