kingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">LauriPatterson</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We have generally stayed away from the bullish view that has gripped investors about Hormel Foods Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HRL\" title=\"Hormel Foods Corporation\">HRL</a></span>). Granted, as the stock has moved lower we have looked for some tactical upside plays. But overall, we saw it as a stock with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1365382318/image_1365382318.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742079-hormel-foods-bears-strike-yet-another-blow", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:45:09"}, {"id": "4742125", "title": "LendingClub: Too Early To Downgrade", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"LendingClub headquarters in Silicon Valley.\" data-id=\"1179464837\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Vi</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As with most fintechs, <strong>LendingClub Corporation</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LC\" title=\"LendingClub Corporation\">LC</a></span>) has seen a big run this year. While the stock is up a lot off the lows, LendingClub is only trading back to a more normalized valuation. My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4688746-lending-club-back-to-growth-mode\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4688746-lending-club-back-to-growth-mode\" target=\"_blank\">investment thesis</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1179464837/image_1179464837.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742125-lendingclub-too-early-to-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:34:30"}, {"id": "4742121", "title": "Coca-Cola: Macro Factors Weigh Since Mid-Year, Keeping A Hold But Raising FV Target", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of two young woman having fun\" data-id=\"1664170199\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Riska</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There's a cart-load full of macro factors impacting food companies in the Consumer Staples sector today. Shares of Coca-Cola (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KO\" title=\"The Coca-Cola Company\">KO</a></span>) plunged from the middle of the third quarter through November. A brief bounce, which included a better-than-week-long </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1664170199/image_1664170199.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742121-coca-cola-macro-factors-weigh-since-mid-year-keeping-a-hold-but-raising-fv-target", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:27:25"}, {"id": "4742092", "title": "Monte Rosa Therapeutics: A First Assessment", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man, computer screen and dna \u200bfor lab research for gene therapy or anti aging science, futuristic or innovation. Male person, pointing and double helix for medical technology, chromosome or mutation\" data-id=\"2148853415\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1069px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bevan Goldswain</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of molecular glue degrader therapy concern <strong>Monte Rosa Therapeutics, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLUE\" title=\"Monte Rosa Therapeutics, Inc.\">GLUE</a></span>)</strong> rallied very strongly after <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4213044-monte-rosa-jumps-on-150m-license-deal-with-novartis\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4213044-monte-rosa-jumps-on-150m-license-deal-with-novartis\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>announcing</strong> </a>a partnership with <strong>Novartis (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVS\" title=\"Novartis AG\">NVS</a>)</strong> on October 28, 2024. With $150 million upfront, it marks its second collaboration in the past twelve months, validating the attractiveness of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148853415/image_2148853415.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742092-monte-rosa-therapeutics-a-first-assessment", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:21:24"}, {"id": "4742120", "title": "EWG: Facing Growth Challenges And May Exhibit Higher Volatility", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1648469312/image_1648469312.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man taking a photo of friends jumping in front of Brandenburg gate on vacation\" data-id=\"1648469312\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1648469312/image_1648469312.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1648469312/image_1648469312.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1648469312/image_1648469312.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1648469312/image_1648469312.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.co